OL,3,CHospital declares critical incident
OL,4,Cfor the fifth time this year
OL,6,FDerriford Hospital in Plymouth has
OL,7,Fdeclared a critical incident for the
OL,8,Ffifth time in 2024.
OL,10,FThe measure, which was brought in at
OL,11,F8am on 4 April, is the highest state
OL,12,Fof alert for a hospital and means that
OL,13,Fadditional steps are taken to ensure
OL,14,Fpatient safety.
OL,16,FThe NHS trust that runs the site said
OL,17,Fthe incident has been announced due to
OL,18,Fincreased operational pressures and IT
OL,19,Fissues affecting the hospital's 'key
OL,20,Fclinical systems'.
