OL,6,FIt added that people attending A&E who
OL,7,Fdo not have emergency or life-
OL,8,Fthreatening conditions may be sent to
OL,9,Fother healthcare services, as the
OL,10,Femergency department is 'very full'.
OL,12,FStaff say anyone who is unwell should
OL,13,Finstead call NHS 111 or use NHS 111
OL,14,Fonline, where they may be provided
OL,15,Fwith advice or redirected to other
OL,16,Fsites, such as the minor injury units
OL,17,Fin Tavistock and Kingsbridge.
