OL,3,CHospital declares critical incident
OL,4,Cfor the fifth time this year
OL,6,FBut University Hospitals Plymouth NHS
OL,7,FTrust added that those with a 'very
OL,8,Fserious or life-threatening emergency'
OL,9,Fshould still attend A&E.
OL,11,FThe hospital has declared a critical
OL,12,Fincident five times since the start of
OL,13,Fthe year, with the first incident
OL,14,Fbeing announced just five days into
OL,15,F2024. At that time, staff said it was
OL,16,Fdue to higher numbers of people
OL,17,Fattending A&E over the previous three
OL,18,Fdays.
