OL,3,CHospital declares critical incident
OL,4,Cfor the fifth time this year
OL,6,FThey declared a second incident later
OL,7,Fin January, which lasted for eight
OL,8,Fdays, and a third in February, which
OL,9,Flasted for three days, after high
OL,10,Fnumbers of people with the flu
OL,11,Fstretched capacity at Derriford
OL,12,FHospital.
OL,14,FStaff then declared a fourth critical
OL,15,Fincident on the afternoon of Sunday 10
OL,16,FMarch due to 'high occupancy' in the
OL,17,Fhospital.
